These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | scientific |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |
| Sport   | rowing | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-5-3::.
